Chicken Cutlet cooked until burnt. Fries are so miserable.  1st and last time buying from this store

Decent portion size for the cheapest fish and chips I ever seen. It's also served really fast like less than 5 mins and the plate looks good. Not a fan of fries so not bothered by the small amount. Fries aren't healthy anyway and u can get a lot from fast food chains. It's not bad for $6 if you are looking for a lighter western meal.
Ordered fish and chips at 5.50. The aunty told me to wait 7min to collect as there are a few orders in front of me. The fish and chips is normal standard. Probably could have provide more fries.
Just a normal Fish and Chips, nothing astounding. Fries quantity was pathetic, should have provided more.
